 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1855202dd6664e5b99d499df35cee258e10f95","tid":1225274,"uid":241889,"like":6,"dislike":25,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"睇完標題就負皮咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aec4cbe0dd546bfb94cfcf3266bb690a436fb9b","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6.16見</span></span>"},{"pid":"34f4eab6e1a3f66f39f1868fdd7180cffa7e52ae","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有放番義士岀嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbbb5e7b0e2b4b926e1e6b57d4ca1ef865fe0f0e","tid":1225274,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32815083c587ecb3f8f720079ad1955a82ede1c","tid":1225274,"uid":13754,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"616重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動指控<br />\n3. 撤銷對手無寸鐵、和平示威者之起訴<br />\n<br />\n另加一個<br />\n撤銷官員、警察及損害香港民主人權者進入外國旅遊、工作或居留的權利"},{"pid":"bcc8696412a5c9a33db7b35f35a44f6b8f4a52c1","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">黑警道歉</span></span>"},{"pid":"15f82e3c94ab239b15e6e0efbf8571aff68f8683","tid":1225274,"uid":125727,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n道歉都冇句!? 仲覺得自己岩 被逼暫緩?<br />\n社會反政府 用難過 同 遺憾 ? <br />\n<br />\n缺不收貨!"},{"pid":"50e8694ebde494cfff97b7eaabdc0c657cc274a7","tid":1225274,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce0e9fb9491a0cbe7933912f88858394fa6f002","tid":1225274,"uid":11644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47338289a775c628523ea3fb6eb0ca7dd7eed395","tid":1225274,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"要撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633ea970e70eab579183a54704815a657cd8f310","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">聽日咁多位巴絲企爆港島，嚇到林鄭撤回</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad8c34340073172d261a5f9688407e1076020d2","tid":1225274,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"聽日不見不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88044024bc55ebbbcc7d16762539c44b91d87333","tid":1225274,"uid":87414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"不要暫緩，要撤回。人生沒有那麼多時間給你拖時間。不撤就去抗議，憤怒就去遊行。中央有什麼用還是會被美國打。爭取不到就勇武，翻臉就殺了她。大不了被狗打，你連出來都不敢還好意思說愛香港。警局放你出來之後找到林鄭要求撤回，要求撤回到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你要求撤回。"},{"pid":"3f9e32b3f2d825e785d41e43c036a6ef2a220f4a","tid":1225274,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（希望大家廣傳民陣fb呼籲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n有港台司機比警察用槍射頭一度心臟停頓，有女拔萃男教師比警察用槍射中眼喪失視力，有患第三期肺癌老人比警察用槍射中，亦有更多後生仔比警察圍毆毒打！<br />\n<br />\n宜家只係暫緩而非撤回，好明顯政府係玩緊施字訣，等你班愚民放下戒心再揾一日直接交上立法會一日之內二讀三讀過咗條逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘香港人鮮血嘅付出，我地唔可以比佢地嘅血白流，誓必撤回逃犯條例！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣反送中遊行</span><br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<span style=\"color: gold;\">（有可能再加入其他起點同時前進，請留意民陣fb最新消息）</span><br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣三罷反送中集會</span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（留意返星期一嘅三罷集會係未有時間，要等民陣fb睇下佢地點安排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span>"},{"pid":"52bad71f6e9dcb700938505998ad520961039089","tid":1225274,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"暫緩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係等大家冇咁火嘅時候就推返出嚟"},{"pid":"5f8a87d2b4912e3df3e67c8a402a28a5f1043c25","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">而家唔岀，以後冇得岀</span></span>"},{"pid":"f805ec8db1b1b01e309a8edb1f74b7093e68031b","tid":1225274,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"釋放義士 追究使用過份武力警犬"},{"pid":"577428a0456daab989639153951bf9286716cbff","tid":1225274,"uid":260870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608c932e03db0830be4fec49e1ee7dd83d4436c","tid":1225274,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi