216b451","tid":1225274,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.privacytools.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.privacytools.io%2F&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=b7c1719a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.privacytools.io/</a><br />\n想上網安全既巴打可以入去睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6abb3819238e53a77ad1f11f629c5ddb3cfd038","tid":1225274,"uid":258484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"我愛林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令香港大和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令新一代更團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令大家更加有決心企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭是瑰寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢嘅子孫世世代代都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">616 黑衫遊行 到時見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"546425c2edf85b5416389c0815c3c3d5db837671","tid":1225274,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"不要暫緩，要撤回。人生沒有那麼多時間給你拖時間。不撤就去抗議，憤怒就去遊行。中央有什麼用還是會被美國打。爭取不到就勇武，翻臉就殺了她。大不了被狗打，你連出來都不敢還好意思說愛香港。警局放你出來之後找到林鄭要求撤回，要求撤回到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你要求撤回。 &mdash;-香港人"},{"pid":"0a2ae3da13f9823b83a659e6494d60f206d8d6c2","tid":1225274,"uid":122110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"黑色衫，聽日見"},{"pid":"1391b748efa0cdf36155034c1300449bb7539652","tid":1225274,"uid":76133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uUVgRMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuUVgRMt.png&h=42c5b494&s={SIZE}\" /