台 &gt; 落實普選 &gt; 討論香港可行前景（例如獨立/永續基本法）"},{"pid":"a3458cd3fc9f73266b29bf2c1e3971e41a73938c","tid":1225274,"uid":234831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭態度仲係咁強硬</span></strong>"}]}